      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence criteria tightened to 1e-6 for all residuals; floating-point round-off analysis documented for hemolysis scalar accumulation over long particle tracks.",
      "rationale": "Solver error assessment was flagged as an epistemic gap at MRL 5. Iterative residuals were reported at 1e-4 only; no round-off analysis was performed for particle-tracking hemolysis accumulation. Factor not assessed."
    },
