      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of simulation setup by a second analyst; documented checklist covering mesh import, boundary condition assignment, and post-processing scripts.",
      "rationale": "No independent analyst review was performed. Use error is an unresolved epistemic gap at MRL 5; factor not assessed."
