      "acceptanceCriteria": "Systematic evaluation of turbulence model selection (SST k-omega vs. RSM) and hemolysis constitutive model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger vs. Zhang) impact on predicted hemolysis index.",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty was identified as a critical epistemic gap. Only one turbulence model and one hemolysis constitutive model were used; no sensitivity study was conducted. Factor not assessed."
