      "acceptanceCriteria": "Monte Carlo or polynomial chaos expansion quantifying sensitivity of hemolysis index to blood viscosity, red blood cell volume fraction, and inlet velocity profile uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Although Monte Carlo UQ was initiated, convergence was not achieved within the study timeline due to computational cost. Input uncertainty characterisation remains an epistemic gap at MRL 5; factor not assessed."
    },
