      "acceptanceCriteria": "Statistical sample size justification for bench experiments; minimum n=5 independent runs per operating point with inter-run variability reported.",
      "rationale": "Experimental sample sizes were not documented in the validation report; inter-run variability data were unavailable. Test sample characterisation is an unresolved epistemic gap; factor not assessed."
